lu.uni.geko.util.tostring
Class ToString

java.lang.Object
  lu.uni.geko.util.tostring.ToString
Direct Known Subclasses:
EMFToString
public class ToString
extends Object

A utility class for providing custom string representations similar to the default Object.toString().

(Note that although this class itself does not use the fact that it allows instances of it to be created we had to resort to this solution in order to make it possible to override behaviour. If Java would allow static methods to be overridden (nobody knows how) we could implement this the way a utility class should be implemented.)
